Paper: hep-th/9309106

Date: 1993-09-20

Title: Gravitational Dressing of Renormalization Group

Authors: I. R. Klebanov, I. I. Kogan and A. M. Polyakov

Comments: preprint PUPT-1421 10 pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev.Lett. 71 (1993) 3243-3246

We study the gravitational dressing of renormalizable two-dimensional fieldtheories. Our main result is that the one-loop $\beta$-function is finitelyrenormalized by the factor ${k+2\over k+1}$, where $k$ is the central charge ofthe gravitational $SL(2, R)$ current algebra.